{"tid":1714451,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解從來冇人搞灣仔、會展","createTime":"2019-11-13T01:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:26:40.000Z","uid":232488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aadddd523e99862c6796825ba2cb3fe9c3f2f073","tid":1714451,"uid":232488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:24:19.000Z","msg":"[black]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd37127a57a3662042f710b63a682ed3481b6cf","tid":1714451,"uid":310612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:28:56.000Z","msg":"展覽業對香港極之重要求下大家千祈唔好搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9181c32eab311403bcb08b4690769fb78a926639","tid":1714451,"uid":278228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:33:45.000Z","msg":"借po一個位<br />\n大家好，示威其實都4個月<br />\n我地每次行動都會影響到民生，<br />\n琴日我係沙田去暴大，<br />\n沿途好多街彷屌road block，又話過分乜乜77<br />\n但冇人提過黑警好似殺人咁攻中大<br />\n因為呢件事<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔關佢事</span></strong></span><br />\n每次咁辛苦做咁多野，到頭嚟都係要比人屌<br />\n既然係咁，<br />\n大家係咪時候諗下要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直搗皇龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔關政見問題，係有的確為所不少既人只關注生計<br />\n同有冇屋企番，甚至會主動清road block<br />\n即使唔係撐警<br />\n既然守中大又要送頭，守旺角又要通頂<br />\n但係都迫唔到政府做啲乜<br />\n<br />\n4個月喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解宜家仲唔升級去搞啲官</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n至少仲會多人支持<br />\n<br />\n策略：小隊突擊，人在明我在暗<br />\n<br />\n要救中大就要有大啲話語權，宜家有話語權既係官"},{"pid":"dc64c501e0fe293968c4c3f5bb38b473e977a9e7","tid":1714451,"uid":278228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-1